EXERCISE-2

Part A
-Create a file "hello.txt"  in your present working directory.
-Rename it as "hello .sh"
-Make this file executable only by the owner

Solution:

touch hello.txt
mv hello.txt hello.sh
chmod u=rwx hello.sh

Part B
